(179, '<ul>\r\n	<li>Waiver re-approved on 11/20/2018; effective 11/20/2018 to 9/30/2023</li>\r\n	<li>Waiver originally approved on 1/12/2018; U.S. District Court invalidated CMS&rsquo;s original approval on 6/29/2018 for failing to consider how the waiver furthered the objectives of the Medicaid program and remanded the waiver back to CMS for additional review; waiver application, amendment application, and STCs completed additional public comment period on 8/18/2018</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, 15, 1, '2018-11-12 12:26:51', '2019-03-26 08:40:56', NULL, NULL),
