(117, '<ul><li> Demonstration authorizes stateâ€™s mandatory MMC program, among other features\n</li><li> Waiver amendment seeks to provide pre-tenancy and tenancy supportive housing services</li>\nfor individuals ages 18+ who are any of the following:\no Chronically homeless\no Homeless/at risk of homelessness and have a severe MH disorder, SUD, or chronic/\ncomplex health needs\no Homeless/at risk of homelessness and have frequent ED visits or inpatient hospital\nstays </ul>', '', 18, 6, NULL, NULL, '2018-11-03 09:43:10', '2018-11-03 09:43:10'),
