(119, '<ul><li> Proposed supportive housing benefits include:\n<p>o Pre-tenancy supports (include screening and assessment, development of housing\nsupport plan, assistance with housing search, application preparation and submission,\nand moving assistance, among other services)^</p>\n<p>o Tenancy supports (include individual housing and tenancy-sustaining services,\neducation and training, teaching dispute resolution with landlords and neighbors, and\nservice care coordination, among other services)^</p></li>\n<li> Other current SUD benefits include:\n<p>o Residential SUD services</p>\n<p>o Outpatient SUD services</p>\n<p>o Methadone treatment</p></li></ul> ', '', 18, 8, NULL, NULL, '2018-11-03 09:43:10', '2018-11-03 09:43:10'),
