(132, '<ul>\r\n	<li>&ldquo;Global waiver&rdquo; encompassing almost entire Medicaid program</li>\r\n	<li>Authorizes mandatory MMC-like program (described in more detail below) and &ldquo;investments&rdquo; in initiatives that increase access to care, improve outcomes, and reduce the uninsured and underinsured populations, among other features</li>\r\n	<li>Approved &ldquo;investments&rdquo; include initiatives related to treating SUD and promoting BH integration</li>\r\n	<li>Aligns with November 2017 SMD letter; state provides a full continuum of SUD benefits and has obtained a waiver of the IMD exclusion</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, 21, 6, NULL, NULL, '2018-11-03 10:00:56', '2018-11-03 10:00:56'),
