(135, '<p>Unable to locate</p>', '<p>Unable to locate</p>', '<p>&ldquo;Prescription Drug coverage will be provided by the CONTRACTORs according to the Member&rsquo;s needs. The pharmacy benefit provided by the CONTRACTOR must comply with the coverage and benefit guidelines set forth in section 1927(k)(2) of the Social Security Act. The Department shall, at its discretion, exclude specific medications or classes of medications from the CONTRACTOR&rsquo;s responsibility. These exclusions shall be communicated and adjusted for through the capitation rate setting process.&rdquo;</p>', '<p>South Carolina Medicaid Managed Care Contract</p>', 23, 1, 9, '1', '1', '1', '2018-11-17 10:05:23', '2018-11-20 10:34:07', '<p><a href="https://msp.scdhhs.gov/managedcare/sites/default/files/2018%20MCO%20Contract%20-%20Final.pdf">South Carolina Medicaid Managed Care Contract</a></p>'),
