naged Care &ndash; July 2018</a></p>'),
(261, NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Claims-level Indicators:</strong><br />\r\nMCOs are required to submit paid encounters for pharmacy products in the National Council for Prescription Drug Programs Batch format</p>', '<p>WA Health Care Authority Apple Health &ndash; Fully Integrated Managed Care &ndash; July 2018 (page 93)</p>', 44, 1, 11, '1', '2', '1', '2018-11-19 10:03:53', '2018-11-20 12:36:06', '<p><a href="https://www.hca.wa.gov/assets/billers-and-providers/ipbh_fullyintegratedcare_medicaid.pdf">WA Health Care Authority Apple Health &ndash; Fully Integrated Managed Care &ndash; July 2018 (page 93)</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
