(876, '""Telemedicine" means the practice of health care delivery, diagnosis, consultation, evaluation and treatment, transfer of medical data or exchange of medical education information by means of a two-way, real-time interactive communication, not to exclude store and forward technologies, between a patient and a physician with access to and reviewing the patient\'s relevant clinical information prior to the telemedicine visit." ', 'Referred to as "TeleHealth" in the SoonerCare Medicaid program ', 'OK SB726 ', 'https://legiscan.com/OK/text/SB726/id/1608914/Oklahoma-2017-SB726-Enrolled.pdf', '1', 246, 1, 1, '1', '2018-11-12 12:09:10', '2018-11-22 16:41:50'),
