(100, 3, 'AZ', 'Question', 'Must a telepresenter or health care provider be present with a patient during a telemedicine encounter?', 'No ', 'The telepresenter may be present but is not required to be present. ', 'AHCCS FFS Provider Manual, Ch. 10: Professional and Technical Services, (10-29). ', 'https://www.azahcccs.gov/PlansProviders/Downloads/FFSProviderManual/FFS_Chap10.pdf', '2018-11-26 08:21:02', '2018-11-26 08:21:02'),
(101, 3, 'AZ', 'Question', 'Must providers obtain informed consent from a patient prior to a telemedicine encounter?', 'No', 'Consent is required only if a recording of the interactive video is made. ', 'AHCCS Medicaid Policy Manual, Medical Policy for AHCCS Covered Services, Ch. 300, Policy 320: Services with Special Circumstances, (320-23). ', 'https://www.azahcccs.gov/shared/Downloads/MedicalPolicyManual/300/320-I.pdf', '2018-11-26 08:21:02', '2018-11-26 08:21:02'),
