(319, 10, 'GA', 'Question', 'Details on innovative payment and service delivery models or other state programs that include telehealth.', 'Georgia Partnership for TeleHealth (GPT)  is the leading agency in Georgia focusing on increasing access to healthcare through the innovative use of technology including telemedicine, health information exchange and telehealthâ€¦ The program began with 8 patient visits in 2006 and grew to over 75,000 in 2012 and more than 240,000 in 2014. GPTâ€™s original Open Access Network now includes over 600 locations with over 200 specialists and healthcare partners and providers that represent over 30 specialties.', NULL, 'About Georgia Partnership for Telehealth. ', 'http://www.gatelehealth.org/georgia-partnership-for-telehealth/', '2018-11-26 08:21:02', '2018-11-26 08:21:02'),
