(944, 29, 'NH', 'Question', 'Does the state limit Medicaid reimbursement for telemedicine services based on the type of provider facilitating the telemedicine encounter?', 'Yes', 'Physician; Physician Assistant; Nurse Practitioner; Clinical Nurse Specialist; Nurse Midwife; Clinical Psychologist; Clinical Social Worker; Registered Dietitian or Nutrition Professional.', '42 C.F.R. section 410.78 ', 'https://www.gpo.gov/fdsys/pkg/CFR-2011-title42-vol2/pdf/CFR-2011-title42-vol2-sec410-78.pdf ', '2018-11-26 08:21:04', '2018-11-26 08:21:04'),
