(953, 29, 'NH', 'Question', 'Does the state Medicaid program apply any geographic restrictions to telemedicine encounters?', 'Yes', 'All eligible originating sites must be located in either rural professional shortage areas or outside the Metropolitan Statistical Area.', '42 C.F.R. section 410.78 ', 'https://www.gpo.gov/fdsys/pkg/CFR-2011-title42-vol2/pdf/CFR-2011-title42-vol2-sec410-78.pdf ', '2018-11-26 08:21:04', '2018-11-26 08:21:04'),
