(1594, 50, 'WY', 'Question', 'Does the state Medicaid program limit coverage and reimbursement for telemedicine to a prescribed set of health conditions or services?', 'Yes', 'Eligible services include:\n Consultations\nOffice or other outpatient visits\nPsychotherapy\nPsychiatric diagnostic interview examination\nNeurobehavioral status exam\nEnd stage renal disease related-services\nIndividual medical nutrition\ntherapy\nMental Health and Substance Abuse Treatment Services\nRemote Cochlear Implant', 'WY Dept. of Public Health Insurance, Medicaid, CMS 1500\nICD-10, p. 113 (Revised April 5, 2018).', 'https://wymedicaid.portal.conduent.com/manuals/Manual_CMS1500_4_5_18.pdf', '2018-11-26 08:21:05', '2018-11-26 08:21:05'),
(1595, 50, 'WY', 'Question', 'Does the state Medicaid program limit the frequency with which they will reimburse for telemedicine services for a given patient?', 'No', NULL, 'WY Dept. of Public Health Insurance, Medicaid, CMS 1500\nICD-10, p. 113 (Revised April 5, 2018).', 'https://wymedicaid.portal.conduent.com/manuals/Manual_CMS1500_4_5_18.pdf', '2018-11-26 08:21:05', '2018-11-26 08:21:05'),
(1596, 50, 'WY', 'Question', 'Does the state Medicaid plan restrict or provide exceptions for services provided via telemedicine for end-stage renal disease or dialysis? (e.g., in-person check-ups between treatments)', 'Yes', 'For ESRD-related services, at least one (1) face-to-face, â€œhands onâ€\nvisit (not telehealth) must be furnished each month to examine the\nvascular access site by a qualified provider.', 'WY Dept. of Public Health Insurance, Medicaid, CMS 1500\nICD-10, p. 115 (Revised April 5, 2018).', 'https://wymedicaid.portal.conduent.com/manuals/Manual_CMS1500_4_5_18.pdf', '2018-11-26 08:21:05', '2018-11-26 08:21:05'),
